CAREFREE WINES FROM EVERYWHERE

WINE pre-dates recorded history and is grown almost every- where. If you are looking for the great wines of the world you will not find them below. However, you will find—in an age of spiralling wine prices—several good, satisfying examples that will not make too serious a dent in the family budget. Some of these will represent previously untried journeys into wine drinking—an Odyssey worth undertaking, particularly in the summer when there is freedom and leisure to move into the by-paths of the wine world. These wines are not endowed with fame and recognition—but each will have its own personal message.
